formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
1	The Details of Estimated cost is taken on the basis of details provided by management															
2	The actual cost incurred and paid is taken as per books of accounts															
3	The unit consideration of the units where no AFS or Allotment letter or sale deed is done are taken as provided by the management															
4	As per GHB'S rules and regulations the Estate Manager first receives the money from beneficiaries in their account than they transfer the amount in GHB's head office account. Head office-GHB transfer the amount in Executive Engineer's account for making payment to Agency.The above mentioned account is Executive Engineer bank account															
5	Money received from Allottes are not deposited in RERA Account															
6	The Actual carpet area of residential unit is 26.6 Sq. Mts instead of 28.5 Sq. Mts and Area of exclusive balcony / verandah (Sq.Mts.) is 1.9 Sq. Mts instead of 26.6 Square Meter.Gujarat Housing board need to rectify the same.
